          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: var(--s-5); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.7; list-style: none;">
            <li>&rarr; <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/sales-professionals/">All sales professional mortgage programs</a></li>
